OL,3,C435 jobs to go at Sensodyne maker
OL,4,CHaleon as it plans to shut UK factory
OL,6,FMore than 400 jobs are to be axed at
OL,7,FSensodyne toothpaste and Advil
OL,8,Fpainkillers firm Haleon as it plans to
OL,9,Fshut its only manufacturing site in
OL,10,Fthe UK.
OL,12,FThe consumer healthcare group, which
OL,13,Fwas spun out of drugs giant GSK in
OL,14,F2022, is shutting its factory in
OL,15,FMaidenhead, Berkshire, which will
OL,16,Faffect the 435 staff at the site.
OL,18,FIt is aiming to close the operation on
OL,19,Fa phased basis over the next two years
OL,20,Fbut stressed that the plans are being
OL,21,Fconsulted on.
