OL,3,C435 jobs to go at Sensodyne maker
OL,4,CHaleon as it plans to shut UK factory
OL,6,FThe factory makes some of the FTSE 100
OL,7,Flisted firm's toothpaste and mouthwash
OL,8,Fbrands, such as Sensodyne and
OL,9,FParodontax.
OL,11,FHaleon, which employs nearly 2,000
OL,12,Fstaff in the UK, will transfer some of
OL,13,Fthe production to its site in Slovakia.
OL,15,FA spokesman for Haleon said:
OL,16,F"Following a strategic review of our
OL,17,Fglobal manufacturing capabilities, we
OL,18,Fhave determined that our Maidenhead
OL,19,Fsite is no longer a viable option for
OL,20,Fthe manufacture of our products.
