OL,6,F"We have therefore taken the difficult
OL,7,Fdecision to begin a phased closure of
OL,8,Fthe site over a two-year period,
OL,9,Fsubject to consultation.
OL,11,F"This decision was not taken lightly,
OL,12,Fand our priority is to ensure that the
OL,13,Fpeople impacted are supported through
OL,14,Fthis process."
