OL,3,C435 jobs to go at Sensodyne maker
OL,4,CHaleon as it plans to shut UK factory
OL,6,FFollowing the closure, it will have a
OL,7,Fcorporate office in Weybridge, Surrey,
OL,8,Fand a corporate office in London,
OL,9,Fwhile it is also investing #130
OL,10,Fmillion in a new research and
OL,11,Fdevelopment site in Weybridge. It has
OL,12,F25 factories worldwide.
OL,14,FThe firm was formed in 2019 by the
OL,15,Fmerger of the consumer healthcare
OL,16,Fbusinesses of British pharmaceutical
OL,17,Fgroup GSK and US rival Pfizer, sitting
OL,18,Fas a joint venture within GSK.
