OL,6,FIt was then spun out of GSK as a
OL,7,Fstandalone business listed on the
OL,8,FLondon Stock Exchange in July 2022.
OL,10,FGSK and Pfizer have since sold down
OL,11,Ftheir stakes in the company, with the
OL,12,Fpair owning 4.2% and about 24%
OL,13,Frespectively.
OL,15,FHaleon has been pressing ahead with
OL,16,Fplans to cut its debts, rein in costs
OL,17,Fand sell off brands to simplify the
OL,18,Fbusiness.
